# ezpermissions

A simple and efficient Discord permission checker that helps you validate user permissions effortlessly! ğŸš€

## âœ¨ Features

- ğŸ”§ **Quick Setup** â€“ Easily integrate permission checks into your bot.
- ğŸ› **Full Permission Coverage** â€“ Supports all Discord permissions.
- âœ… **True_ & False_ Checks** â€“ Validate if a user has or lacks a permission.
- ğŸ“¦ **Lightweight & Easy to Use** â€“ No complex setup required.

